## Example

The following example generates C3038:

```cpp
// C3038.cpp
// compile with: /openmp /c
int g_i, g_i2;

int main() {
   int i;

   #pragma omp parallel reduction(+: g_i)
   {
      #pragma omp for private(g_i)   // C3038
      // try the following line instead
      // #pragma omp for private(g_i2)
      for (i = 0; i < 10; ++i)
